    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, which exemplifies a harmonious balance of performance and reliability. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure that its mechanical integrity and presentation meet the standards of the most discerning motorists. Featuring a refined interior and a robust powertrain, this vehicle offers a sophisticated driving experience and represents a superlative value proposition within its class. We invite serious inquiries to experience the caliber of this exceptional offering firsthand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
